sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Uzytkownik
    participant CLI as DietPlannerCLI
    participant NS as NutritionService
    participant MP as MealPlannerService
    participant MR as MealRepository
    participant SL as ShoppingListService

    U->>CLI: Wybiera "Generuj plan tygodniowy"
    CLI->>U: Prosi o dane profilu
    U->>CLI: Podaje profil
    CLI->>MP: create_weekly_plan(profile)
    MP->>MR: filter_by_preferences(preferences)
    MR-->>MP: lista posilkow
    MP->>NS: estimate_daily_calories(profile)
    NS-->>MP: cel kalorii
    MP->>NS: estimate_macro_target(profile, calories)
    NS-->>MP: cel makro
    MP-->>CLI: WeeklyPlan
    CLI-->>U: Pokazuje podsumowanie

    U->>CLI: Wybiera liste zakupow
    CLI->>SL: build_for_week(plan)
    SL-->>CLI: liczba skladnikow
    CLI-->>U: Wyswietla liste zakupow
